<p><a name="Historic" id="Historic"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Book_of_Mormon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Historic">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Historic</span></h3>
